<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Nestor" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Nestor,</orth> 1) the oldest and wisest hero before Troy: <bibl n="shak. luc 1401" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1401</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. luc 1401" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1401</bibl> <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.169" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 3, 169</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 1.1.56" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. I, 1, 56</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.2.188" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 2, 188</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.32" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 32</bibl> etc. 2) Name of an attendant of Pericles: <bibl n="shak. per 3.1.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. III, 1, 66</bibl>.
